name: The Angie Files - Episode 1 - "Cyber Knife"
description: In 2011, my mom, Angie Fetterley moved from Rockford, Illinois to live with me in Los Angeles after her left kidney was removed due to a primary renal cell cancer. She has since had a brain tumor removed, her left lung removed, and her colon removed. Today, 4/16/21, she completed her 5th day of a radiation treatment called the Cyber Knife to remove another tumor in her remaining lungs. She is one tuff cookie, and likes to file her dentures to custom fit. Here's to another 10 years, mom! <3
